      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/carpaint.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330604731&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223474/carpaint.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330604731&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"200\" data-width=\"200\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223548\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"carpaint.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223474\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"573cd174-663e-441a-bb92-12c9d197dd34\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/carpaint.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330604731&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/carpaint.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330604731&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 1x\"></span><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Car Paint with flakes and coating.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p>Produces a bumped normal that simulates flake-like results in specular or reflective material effects. Connecting this to a the Bump Normal parameter of PxrSurface can create metallic fleck paint.</p><h3 id=\"PxrFlakes-InputParameters\">Input Parameters</h3><h4 id=\"PxrFlakes-InputNormal\">Input Normal</h4><p>Connect your bump pattern here if you wish to add flakes on top of it. Ignored if not connected.</p><h4 id=\"PxrFlakes-FlakeRandomness\">Flake Randomness</h4><p>This increases the distribution of flake normals, or their deviation from the base normal.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"align-start\" data-local-id=\"bd279f42-8ce2-4d43-9ccd-ce52e29856bb\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"randomness_0.0.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/randomness_0.0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330604731&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223474/randomness_0.0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330604731&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"200\" data-width=\"200\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223545\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"randomness_0.0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223474\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"59d1cbb2-9bf7-4a05-99aa-1bcacdcbe422\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/randomness_0.0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330604731&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/randomness_0.0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330604731&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper conflue