ge-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"size_2.0.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/size_2.0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603867&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223474/size_2.0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603867&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"200\" data-width=\"200\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223497\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"size_2.0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223474\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"597578f6-861e-4871-9593-759629b8539e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/size_2.0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603867&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/size_2.0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603867&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 1x\"></span></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h4 id=\"PxrFlakes-Octaves\">Octaves</h4><p>Number of octaves of noise to calculate flakes. Most of the time, 1 is enough.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"align-start\" data-local-id=\"ad07edfb-c2a6-4922-9785-53f3f12756e0\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"octave_1.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/octave_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223474/octave_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"200\" data-width=\"200\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223494\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"octave_1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223474\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d386576b-0da3-42e5-9562-2d5cd48e336c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/octave_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/octave_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"octave_2.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/octave_2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223474/octave_2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"200\" data-width=\"200\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223491\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"octave_2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223474\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"872b100f-2958-4f4f-9034-0cab6a0b741b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/octave_2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/octave_2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"octave_3.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/octave_3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223474/octave_3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"200\" data-width=\"200\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223488\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"octave_3.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223474\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b20935db-d85a-4f84-9e45-7f5a7f7f1947\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/octave_3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223474/octave_3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330603622&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 1x\"></span></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h4 id=\"PxrFlakes-Jitter\">Jitter</h4><p>Jitters the flake's position. 0.0 gives a grid-like organisation and 1.0 looks very random.</p><h4 id=\"PxrFlakes-ValidateNormals\">Validate Normals</h4><p>Make sure flakes normals are always in the same hemisphere as the original normal.</p><h4 id=\"PxrFlakes-MatchC++patterns\">Match C++ patterns</h4><p>Match RenderMan 23 C++ scenes but may slow down your render.  Use only when necessary.</p><h4 id=\"PxrFlakes-Manifold\">Manifold</h4><p>The manifold over which to apply the flakes.</p><p>The default (when there is no connected manifold) is <code>P</code> in <em>object</em> space. This will work fine if your object is not deforming.<br/>If your object is deforming :</p><ul><li><p>Add a <code>__Pref</code> primvar to your geometry in its un-deformed state.</p></li><li><p>Create a <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542224088/PxrManifold3D\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224088\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrManifold3D</a> node and connect it to the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542223474/PxrFlakes\">PxrFlakes</a> node.</p></li><li><p>In the manifold's <em>Pref</em> field enter: <code>__Pref</code></p></li><li><p>In the manifold's <em>Coordinate System</em> field enter: <code>object</code></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"PxrFlakes-OutputParameters\">Output Parameters</h3><h4 id=\"PxrFlakes-resultN\">resultN</h4><p>The bumped normal.</p><h4 id=\"PxrFlakes-resultA\">resultA</h4><p>The flakes' mask. This is a black and white mask that may allow you to tint flakes or change their roughness, for example.</p>"
    }
